#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:214
msgid ""
"All Spell Cards belong to one School of Magic\\index{Schools of Magic}: "
"either Air, Fire, Earth or Water.  Spells with one School symbol on them are "
"called \\textbf{Basic Spells}\\index{Basic Spell}, while Spells with four "
"identical symbols are called \\textbf{Expert Spells}\\index{Expert Spell}.  "
"\\textbf{Magic Arrow} is a Basic Spell; when casting the \\textbf{Magic "
"Arrow}, you must select which School it belongs to.  By default there's no "
"difference, but certain game effects can refer to specific Schools and to "
"Basic/Expert Spells."
